    <briefdescription>
<para>A checked format string bundled with the caller&apos;s source_location. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The consteval constructor preserves std::format&apos;s compile-time format-string checking while capturing the call site (the std::print/println technique), so the function-style <ref refid="logger_8h_1a1aaf619fc9dbd574aa84dea9e41d3288" kindref="member">Log()</ref> can record an accurate <ulink url="file:line">file:line</ulink> without a macro. Used as a non-deduced parameter so the trailing args drive deduction. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
